description: 2020 Kia Forte LXS — Description (English) This 2020 Kia Forte LXS is powered by a Nu 2.0L inline-4 engine that produces 147 hp and 132 lb-ft of torque and is configured for front-wheel drive. It delivers strong fuel efficiency for daily driving, rated at 29 MPG city and 40 MPG highway. The vehicle is in excellent overall condition and comes with a clean CARFAX report. Factory-standard features (typical equipment): - Powertrain and chassis: Nu 2.0L I4 engine, front-wheel drive, standard stability and traction control systems, and anti-lock braking (ABS). - Safety: Multiple airbags (front, side, and curtain), rearview camera, tire pressure monitoring system (TPMS), and standard electronic safety aids designed to help with vehicle control. - Exterior: Practical, compact sedan proportions with halogen headlamps and daytime running lights, body-colored mirrors and door handles, and factory wheels with all-season tires. - Interior and comfort: Seating for five with durable cloth upholstery, manually adjustable front seats, split-folding rear seat for expanded cargo flexibility, automatic climate control or manual air conditioning depending on factory configuration, power windows and door locks, and a tilt-and-telescoping steering column. - Convenience and electronics: Factory infotainment system with a touchscreen that supports Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, Bluetooth hands-free connectivity, USB input(s) for device charging and media, steering-wheel-mounted audio and phone controls, and cruise control. This Forte LXS offers a balanced combination of fuel economy, straightforward functionality, and the essential safety and technology features expected from a compact sedan. The vehicle’s clean CARFAX and excellent overall condition make it a reliable choice for everyday use. Descripción 2020 Kia Forte LXS — (Español) Este Kia Forte LXS 2020 está equipado con un motor Nu 2.0L de cuatro cilindros en línea que entrega 147 hp y 132 lb-ft de torque, con tracción delantera. Ofrece una buena economía de combustible para el uso diario, con calificaciones de 29 MPG en ciudad y 40 MPG en carretera. El vehículo se encuentra en excelente estado general y cuenta con un informe CARFAX limpio. Equipamiento de fábrica (equipamiento típico): - Tren motriz y chasis: motor Nu 2.0L I4, tracción delantera, sistemas estándar de control de estabilidad y tracción, y frenos con sistema antibloqueo (ABS). - Seguridad: Múltiples airbags (frontales, laterales y de cortina), cámara de reversa, sistema de monitoreo de presión de neumáticos (TPMS) y ayudas electrónicas estándar para asistir en el control del vehículo. - Exterior: Silueta práctica de sedán compacto con faros halógenos y luces diurnas, espejos y manijas del color de la carrocería, y ruedas de fábrica con neumáticos para todas las estaciones. - Interior y confort: Capacidad para cinco ocupantes con tapicería de tela resistente, asientos delanteros con ajuste manual, asiento trasero abatible en secciones para mayor flexibilidad de carga, aire acondicionado (manual o automático según la configuración de fábrica), elevalunas y cerraduras eléctricos, y columna de dirección con ajuste de inclinación y alcance. - Conveniencia y electrónica: Sistema de infoentretenimiento de fábrica con pantalla táctil compatible con Apple CarPlay y Android Auto, conectividad Bluetooth manos libres, entradas USB para carga y reproducción de medios, controles de audio y teléfono en el volante, y control de crucero. El Forte LXS ofrece un equilibrio entre economía de combustible, funcionalidad directa y las características básicas de seguridad y tecnología que se esperan en un sedán compacto. Su informe CARFAX limpio y su excelente estado general lo convierten en una opción confiable para el uso diario. -- INSTALLED FEATURES: Air filtration, Front air conditioning, Front air conditioning description: Discover the perfect blend of style, efficiency, and technology in this stunning 2020 Volkswagen Jetta 1.4T S. description:
Discover the exceptional 2020 Nissan Altima 2.5 S, a sedan that combines style, performance, and advanced technology to elevate your driving experience. With its sleek black exterior and a host of impressive features, this Altima is poised to exceed your expectations.

Highlighted features of this well-equipped Altima include:

• NissanConnect featuring Apple CarPlay and Android Auto
• Air Conditioning
• Rear window defroster
• Power steering
• Power windows
• Remote keyless entry
• Steering wheel mounted audio controls
• Brake assist
• Electronic Stability Control
• Delay-off headlights
• Fully automatic headlights
• Panic alarm
• Security system

Powered by a reliable 2.5L 4-Cylinder DOHC 16V engine and paired with a smooth CVT with Xtronic transmission, this Altima delivers an impressive fuel economy of 28 MPG in the city and 39 MPG on the highway. With its front-wheel-drive configuration, you'll enjoy confident handling and a comfortable ride, no matter the road conditions.

Step inside the spacious cabin and experience the premium Cloth Seat Trim, which provides exceptional comfort and style. The Altima's advanced technology features, including the AM/FM Audio System with SiriusXM, allow you to stay connected and entertained throughout your journey. The Split folding rear seat offers versatility, while the Power driver seat and Telescoping steering wheel provide a customized driving position.

Safety is paramount in the 2020 Nissan Altima, with features like Dual front impact airbags, Dual front side impact airbags, Knee airbag, Low tire pressure warning, and Occupant sensing airbag ensuring your protection on the road.

This well-maintained Altima with just 91,005 miles represents an excellent value proposition. Imagine the pride and satisfaction of owning a modern, feature-rich sedan that delivers exceptional performance, fuel efficiency, and safety. Experience the difference for yourself by scheduling a test drive today. We're confident you'll be impressed by the 2020 Nissan Altima 2.5 S.

Whether you're running errands around town or embarking on a road trip, this Tesla Model 3 is the perfect companion for any adventure.Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this incredible electric vehicle that offers style, performance, and innovation in one dynamic package. description:
Discover the perfect balance of style, performance, and technology in this exceptional 2020 Ford Fusion Titanium. With its sleek gray exterior and a powerful EcoBoost 2.0L I4 engine paired with all-wheel drive, this sedan is ready to elevate your driving experience.

• NAVIGATION
• SUNROOF/MOONROOF
• LEATHER
• HEATED FRONT SEATS
• BACK-UP CAMERA
• AUTOMATIC TRANSMISSION
• MINI SPARE TIRE

Beyond its impressive capabilities, this Fusion Titanium is equipped with a wealth of premium features that cater to your every need. Sink into the luxurious leather-appointed seats, which are both heated and ventilated, ensuring your comfort in any weather. The intuitive SYNC 3 infotainment system with voice-activated navigation and a premium Sony audio system will keep you connected and entertained on the road.

Thoughtful details like the power moonroof, dual-zone automatic climate control, and a heated steering wheel further enhance the refined driving experience. Safety is also a top priority, with advanced features like forward collision warning, automatic emergency braking, and a 360-degree camera system providing you with added peace of mind.

Designed to impress, this 2020 Ford Fusion Titanium delivers an exceptional blend of style, technology, and performance. With an EPA-estimated 29 MPG on the highway, it's also a smart choice for the environmentally conscious driver. Experience the difference for yourself and schedule a test drive today. We're confident you'll be captivated by this remarkable vehicle.

As you consider your next automotive purchase, remember that our team of knowledgeable sales professionals is here to assist you every step of the way. We're dedicated to ensuring your complete satisfaction, from the moment you step onto our lot to the day you drive off in your dream car. Let us show you why the 2020 Ford Fusion Titanium is the perfect choice for your lifestyle.

Thank you for your interest, and we look forward to the opportunity to earn your business.

This Lifted 2025 Ford F-150 Raptor features a 2.2-inch Eibach Fox 3.0 Stage 2 Progressive Spring Lift, Four Wheel Alignment, 20-inch Vossen Forged HFX-1 Gloss Black Wheels, 37X12.50R20 Nitto Ridge Grappler Tires, Chrome Blackout, and Professionally Installed Window Tint with a Lifetime Warranty. Installed by our Lift Tech, Ricky. *Modifications are optional and are not included in the advertised price.*

Our One Owner and Clean Carfax 2025 Ford F-150 Raptor SuperCrew 4X4 is a bold driving machine built to go almost anywhere in Race Red! Motivated by a Twin-TurboCharged 3.5 Liter High Output EcoBoost V6 supplying 450hp to a 10 Speed Automatic transmission with dedicated off-road modes. They work with exclusive Four Wheel Drive Raptor suspension upgrades, Trail Control, and an electronic locking differential to handle pavement, trails, and uncharted territory, and it returns nearly 18mpg on the highway. Revved-up Raptor design cues include LED lighting, cast-aluminum running boards, hood-mounted heat extractors, fender flares, a twin-panel sunroof, and a bed liner. A Pro Power generator is onboard as well!

Heated and ventilated leather power front seats, heated rear seats, a heated leather steering wheel, dual-zone automatic climate control, and power-adjustable pedals add a touch of comfortable class to our Raptor cabin. Commanding technology awaits with a SYNC-powered infotainment system bundling a 12-inch touchscreen, a 12-inch productivity screen, B&O Unleashed audio, connected navigation compatibility, Apple CarPlay, Android Auto, Bluetooth, and WiFi compatibility.

Ford helps seal the deal with smart safety from blind-spot monitoring, adaptive cruise control, automatic braking, a 360-degree camera system, a head-up display, Pro Trailer Backup Assist, and more. It's no wonder our F-150 Raptor is a top choice for truck professionals worldwide! Save this Page and Call for Availability. We Know You Will Enjoy Your Lifted Trucks Huntsville Test Drive Towards Ownership!

Lifted Trucks has built an unmatched reputation over the last two decades for customizing and selling thousands of the highest quality used vehicles in the country. Our inventory is nationally sourced by our certified buyers who cherry-pick only the best-of-the-best of what is available. These vehicles then go through an 82-point inspection process to guarantee quality and safety.

Our lift kits are installed by our own factory-trained technicians who have thousands of hours of experience. The installation is then inspected by a second dedicated quality-control technician before being sent to our state-of-the-art Hunter Engineering laser alignment rack.

Our aftermarket research and development team always matches the best fitting lift kit, shocks, and wheel & tire combinations to each individual vehicle for optimal off-road performance while maintaining an incredibly smooth ride on the street. We never cut any corners on our builds, which is why we only use top-quality name-brand products when building your Truck, SUV or Jeep.

Lifted Trucks has thousands of 5-star reviews and one of the highest rates of repeat customers in the auto industry. Stop by today and experience the difference!

This is a sedan built for real life â smooth, efficient, and quietly capable whether youâre carving through morning traffic on I-75 in Troy, cruising Woodward Avenue through Birmingham, or heading west on I-94 toward Ann Arbor. Under the hood, the turbocharged 1.5L EcoBoost engine pairs with a 6-speed automatic transmission to deliver responsive acceleration and confident efficiency. It feels composed merging near Telegraph Road in Dearborn and relaxed stretching out across Oakland County backroads. Auto Start-Stop technology keeps things efficient without interrupting the drive, making daily commuting feel effortless. Inside, the Fusion SE keeps everything clean and intuitive. Supportive cloth seating, a power driver seat, rotary gear selector, and a leather-wrapped steering wheel with mounted controls put everything exactly where you expect it. The power sunroof opens the cabin with natural light and fresh air, adding a sense of space whether youâre driving through Royal Oak or cruising quieter neighborhood streets. Dual-zone automatic climate control keeps comfort balanced year-round, while the split-folding rear seat adds flexibility for errands or weekend runs toward Washtenaw County. Technology works quietly in the background, exactly how it should. SYNCÂ infotainment with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto keeps navigation, calls, and music seamless, while Bluetooth connectivity and USB charging keep devices ready. A rearview camera and reverse sensing system simplify tight parking situations around downtown Detroit or busy lots near Somerset Collection. Safety is handled with confidence and clarity. Ford Co-Pilot360â features including Pre-Collision Assist with Automatic Emergency Braking, Lane-Keeping System, Blind Spot Information System, and Cross-Traffic Alert support you whether youâre navigating city streets in Wayne County or cruising south toward Toledo on US-23. From Michigan suburbs to Ohio highways and Indiana corridors like I-69 toward Fort Wayne, the Fusion SE delivers a calm, efficient, and intelligently equipped driving experience that fits real life without trying too hard. Introducing the sleek and stylish 2020 Volkswagen Jetta SE! This stunning sedan combines cutting-edge technology with modern design, making it the perfect choice for those seeking a sophisticated and high-performing vehicle.

Step inside and experience the spacious and luxurious interior, featuring comfortable seating for up to five passengers. With ample legroom and headroom, every journey will be a comfortable one. Plus, the Jetta SE comes equipped with a variety of advanced features such as a touchscreen infotainment system, Bluetooth connectivity, and a rearview camera to make your driving experience even more convenient.

Under the hood, the 2020 Jetta SE boasts a powerful and efficient 1.4-liter turbocharged engine, providing an exhilarating driving experience while still maintaining impressive fuel efficiency. This 2020 Hyundai Elantra SE is a practical and well-equipped compact sedan that offers exceptional value. Boasting a spacious interior, a smooth and efficient powertrain, and a host of desirable features, this Elantra is the perfect choice for the savvy driver seeking a reliable and versatile daily companion.

The dual-zone automatic climate control, power windows, and remote keyless entry add to the vehicle's overall convenience and comfort.

Whether you're seeking a practical daily driver or a versatile family sedan, this 2020 Hyundai Elantra SE is an exceptional choice. description: Introducing the 2020 Kia Forte FE, where style meets substance in a package that promises both reliability and excitement. This stunning sedan, dressed in a pristine white exterior, is not just a car—it's a statement of elegance and efficiency. With its sleek lines and modern design, the Forte FE is sure to turn heads wherever you go. Step inside, and you'll be greeted by a sophisticated gray cloth interior that exudes comfort and class. The thoughtfully designed cabin offers a serene environment, perfect for both short commutes and long journeys. The quality of materials and attention to detail make every drive a luxurious experience, ensuring that you and your passengers travel in style and comfort. Under the hood lies the heart of this remarkable vehicle: the Nu 2.0L I4 engine. With 147 horsepower and 132 ft. lbs. of torque, this engine delivers a spirited performance that makes driving the Forte FE a joy. Whether you're navigating city streets or cruising on the highway, the Continuously Variable Transmission (CVT) ensures smooth and efficient power delivery, enhancing your driving pleasure while maximizing fuel efficiency. What sets the 2020 Kia Forte FE apart is its unparalleled reputation for dependability and quality. It has been recognized by J.D. Power and Associates with the highest ranks in both the Vehicle Dependability Study (VDS) and the Initial Quality Study (IQS). These prestigious awards are a testament to Kia's commitment to engineering excellence and the Forte FE's outstanding reliability. You can drive with confidence, knowing that your vehicle has been rigorously tested and proven to perform at the highest standards. The 2020 Kia Forte FE is not just about performance and reliability, it's also about delivering an exceptional driving experience. The intuitive layout of the controls and the user-friendly interface make it easy to stay connected and entertained on the road. With features designed to enhance your driving experience, the Forte FE ensures that every journey is as enjoyable as the destination. Safety is a top priority in the Forte FE, providing you with peace of mind on every drive. While specific features are not listed, Kia's commitment to safety is well-known, and the Forte FE is engineered to offer protection and security for you and your passengers. In summary, the 2020 Kia Forte FE is the perfect blend of style, performance, and reliability. Its award-winning dependability and quality make it a smart choice for anyone looking for a vehicle that will stand the test of time. The combination of a powerful engine, smooth transmission, and a comfortable interior ensures that every drive is a pleasure. Don't miss your chance to own this exceptional vehicle. What is Wholesale Open to Public? Derrow Shirkey Ford's Wholesale Open to Public is a select offering of used cars that have traditionally been sold at the auction to independent dealers and small used car lots. These are vehicles that fall outside of Derrow Shirkey Ford's used car guidelines. They are generally higher mileage, older, lower-priced vehicles that are perhaps 'flawed' in some way. Some general guidelines for a wholesale vehicle: • They are sold without a warranty • They are offered for a limited time only - 30 days • They are sold 100% AS-IS without any warranty coverage • They are sold with our "best price" posted on the windshield. There is no negotiation necessary. Why Wholesale Open to Public? Simply put - our customers have requested that we make these vehicles available. Many of our customers have a need for basic transportation. By offering a broader selection of "kid's cars", 2nd car, college cars, and other inexpensive transportation options, we feel we can better serve our current customers and the general market.

We are located 2 miles South of the turnpike at exit 13. Our location makes it a very simple drive from Toledo, Fort Wayne, Hillsdale, Angola, Bryan, Defiance, Napoleon, or Jackson. OUR MISSION STATEMENT- We will be honest and transparent. Through teamwork, honesty and hard work, we will build trusting relationships with our customers, always striving to exceed their expectations. The same holds true for our team members as we constantly learn and improve from within ourselves and each other. Come see for yourself why Derrow-Shirkey Ford Lincoln is the fastest growing dealership in the tri-state area. We are committed to making the car buying experience fast, fun and easy!!! 1. Pricing - We post our best price on every vehicle, every day. Period. 2. Trade In’s - We’ll make you a cash offer. No-Nonsense. We will buy your vehicle regardless if you purchase from us or not. 3. Financing - Multiple quotes in minutes. 4. No Surprises - We will gladly provide a history report and a copy of any repairs we performed on the vehicle. 5. Long Distance, No Problem! - We sell vehicles from New York to California.

description:
Embrace style and efficiency with the 2020 Hyundai Elantra SEL, beautifully presented in a vibrant Scarlet Red Pearl finish. This compact sedan features a fuel-efficient 2.0L 4-cylinder DOHC 16V engine paired with a smooth continuously variable transmission (CVT), achieving an impressive 30 MPG in the city and 40 MPG on the highway.

Designed with modern technology and convenience in mind, the Elantra SEL includes Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration, allowing seamless connectivity to your favorite apps while on the go. The exterior parking camera provides enhanced visibility when reversing, making parking easier and safer.

Comfort and ease of use are prioritized with features like heated door mirrors for improved visibility in colder weather, remote keyless entry for added convenience, and speed-sensing steering that adjusts for optimal handling at varying speeds. Enjoy music and controls with ease, thanks to the steering wheel-mounted audio controls.

With a Clean CARFAX and a focus on performance and practicality, the 2020 Hyundai Elantra SEL is the perfect choice for those seeking a reliable and stylish sedan for everyday driving.

description:
Discover the perfect blend of style, performance, and technology in the 2020 Volkswagen Passat 2.0T SE. This sophisticated sedan offers a dynamic driving experience, thoughtful features, and a refined interior that will elevate your daily commute.

Boasting a sleek and modern exterior in striking Black, the Passat 2.0T SE commands attention on the road. Under the hood, the 2.0L I4 TSI Turbocharged engine delivers an exhilarating 6-Speed Automatic with Tiptronic transmission, providing a seamless and responsive driving experience. With an impressive 23 city/34 highway MPG, this Passat balances power and efficiency to keep you moving forward.

• Heated Front Comfort Seats
• Perforated V-Tex Leatherette Seating Surfaces
• VW App-Connect (with Apple CarPlay, Android Auto & MirrorLink)
• Leather-Wrapped Steering Wheel
• Dual-Zone Automatic Climate Control
• Rearview Camera with Dynamic Parking Lines

The 5-speed automatic transmission with overdrive ensures smooth, efficient power delivery, while the front-wheel-drive system provides confident handling and control.

The Accord EX-L is packed with an array of premium features that elevate the driving experience. Enjoy the convenience of keyless entry, the comfort of dual-zone automatic climate control, and the connectivity of the advanced audio system with CD player and satellite radio. The leather-wrapped steering wheel and shift knob add a touch of sophistication, while the power driver's seat and heated front seats provide unparalleled comfort.

This Accord is a certified pre-owned vehicle, meaning it has undergone a rigorous inspection and comes with a comprehensive warranty for your peace of mind. With its low mileage of just 91,225 and impeccable maintenance history, this Accord is ready to provide you with years of reliable, enjoyable driving.

Imagine yourself behind the wheel of this exceptional 2004 Honda Accord EX-L. Experience the perfect blend of performance, technology, and luxury that this vehicle has to offer. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this Accord can enhance your driving experience. We're confident you'll be impressed by its exceptional quality and value.

This sleek and sophisticated sedan is equipped with a powerful Ecotec 1.5L Turbo I4 engine, delivering an impressive 160 horsepower and 184 ft. lbs. of torque. But that's not all, the Malibu LT also comes with a smooth and efficient CVT transmission, ensuring a smooth and seamless driving experience.

Step inside and experience the spacious and modern interior of the Malibu LT. With plenty of legroom and premium materials, you and your passengers will enjoy every ride in comfort and style. And with its versatile split-folding rear seats, you'll have plenty of room for all your cargo needs.

But it's not just about looks and comfort, the Malibu LT is also packed with advanced technology features. From the Chevrolet Infotainment 3 system with an 8-inch touchscreen, to the available built-in 4G LTE Wi-Fi hotspot, you'll always stay connected on the go. Plus, with the convenience of Apple CarPlay and Android Auto compatibility, you can easily access your favorite apps and music.

Safety is always a top priority, and the Malibu LT has you covered with its comprehensive suite of advanced safety features. From Lane Keep Assist and Forward Collision Alert to Rear Cross Traffic Alert and more, you'll have peace of mind on every journey.

description:
Discover the perfect blend of style, efficiency, and affordability with the 2022 Hyundai Accent SE. This compact sedan is the ideal choice for those seeking a reliable and well-equipped vehicle that won't break the bank.

Boasting a sleek white exterior and a host of impressive features, the Accent SE is designed to exceed your expectations. Enjoy the convenience of Handsfree Bluetooth connectivity and the versatility of the USB port, making it easy to stay connected on the go. With the available Option Group 01, you'll have access to a range of desirable amenities, including:

• Handsfree Bluetooth
• USB Port
• 4 Speakers
• AM/FM radio
• Air Conditioning
• Rear window defroster
• Power steering
• Power windows
• Remote keyless entry
• Steering wheel mounted audio controls
• Speed-sensing steering
• Traction control

Under the hood, the Accent SE is powered by a 1.6L I4 PDI DOHC 16V LEV3-ULEV125 engine that delivers an impressive 120 horsepower, coupled with a smooth-shifting CVT transmission and front-wheel drive. With an EPA-estimated 33 mpg in the city and 41 mpg on the highway, this sedan offers exceptional fuel efficiency, allowing you to spend less time at the pump and more time enjoying the open road.

The Accent SE's well-appointed interior features stylish cloth seating, a tilt steering wheel, and a trip computer, providing both comfort and convenience. The split-folding rear seat offers versatile cargo-carrying capabilities, while the Exterior Parking Camera Rear enhances visibility and safety when maneuvering in tight spaces.

Backed by Hyundai's renowned reputation for quality and reliability, the 2022 Accent SE is a smart choice for those seeking a practical and well-equipped vehicle without sacrificing style or performance. Experience the difference for yourself and schedule a test drive today. We're confident you'll be impressed by the Accent SE's exceptional value and the exceptional customer service you'll receive at our dealership.

description:
Introducing the 2007 Lexus ES 350 Base a timeless blend of luxury performance and reliability that continues to stand the test of time. With a pristine white exterior that exudes elegance and sophistication this vehicle is more than just a car, it's a statement. Imagine yourself turning heads on the road as you glide effortlessly in a sedan that embodies both style and substance.

Step inside and you'll be embraced by the inviting warmth of the tan cloth interior. The cabin is designed with your comfort in mind offering a serene and plush environment that makes every journey feel like a first-class experience. Whether you're commuting to work or embarking on a weekend getaway the Lexus ES 350 ensures that you travel in unparalleled comfort.

Under the hood lies the heart of this magnificent machine a robust 3.5L V6 engine that delivers an impressive 272 horsepower and 254 lb-ft of torque. This powertrain promises a driving experience that is both exhilarating and smooth making every drive a memorable one. Paired with a 6-Speed Shiftable Automatic transmission this vehicle offers the perfect balance of power and efficiency allowing you to enjoy spirited drives with the convenience of modern automatic shifting.

With 167 102 miles on the odometer this Lexus ES 350 has been meticulously maintained to ensure it retains its legendary reliability. It's no wonder that this model has been recognized in J.D. Power and Associates's Vehicle Dependability Study (VDS) as a top model. This accolade is a testament to the enduring quality and dependability that Lexus is renowned for providing you with peace of mind and confidence in your purchase.

The 2007 Lexus ES 350 Base is not just about performance and reliability, it's also about the little details that enhance your driving experience. From the sleek lines of its exterior to the thoughtful layout of its interior every aspect of this vehicle has been crafted to elevate your journey. The intuitive controls and ergonomic design ensure that everything you need is within easy reach allowing you to focus on the joy of driving.

Imagine yourself behind the wheel cruising down the highway with the sunroof open feeling the wind in your hair and the sun on your face. The Lexus ES 350 offers an unmatched driving experience that makes even the most mundane trips feel special. Its quiet cabin isolates you from the noise of the outside world creating a sanctuary where you can unwind and enjoy the ride.

In conclusion the 2007 Lexus ES 350 Base is more than just a car, it's a testament to luxury performance and reliability. This vehicle offers everything you could want in a premium sedan and more. Don't miss your chance to own a piece of automotive excellence that has been celebrated for its dependability and timeless appeal. Experience the Lexus ES 350 today and discover why it continues to be a top choice for discerning drivers. Your journey to unparalleled luxury and performance begins here.

description:
The 2007 Chevrolet Impala LT is an impressive full-size sedan that combines spaciousness, comfort, and practicality, making it an ideal choice for families and individuals alike. With its striking Precision Red exterior, the Impala stands out on the road while offering a comfortable and refined driving experience.

Powered by a robust 3.5L V6 engine, this Impala features a 4-speed automatic transmission with overdrive that delivers a smooth ride and adequate power. The vehicle achieves an efficient 20 MPG in the city and 29 MPG on the highway, providing an excellent balance between performance and fuel economy.

Inside, the Impala LT boasts a spacious cabin with a 40/20/40 split-bench seat, making it versatile for different passenger and cargo needs. Key features include a leather-wrapped steering wheel, power sunroof with sunshade, remote keyless entry for added convenience, steering-wheel mounted audio controls for easy access, and a universal home remote for added versatility.

Equipped with 4-wheel anti-lock disc brakes, the Impala LT ensures responsive braking performance, enhancing safety on various road conditions.

This vehicle is a recent arrival to our lot, meticulously maintained and ready for its next journey.

According to KBB.com, "If you’re in search of a big, roomy sedan that won’t break the bank, the newly refined Impala will thoroughly meet your needs and probably exceed your expectations. Also, the SS model makes a good quasi-muscle car for those who require the all-weather advantages of front-wheel drive."

description: Zoom around town in this sleek Silver 2007 Toyota Camry, a true icon on the road. With its reliable 2.4L engine and front-wheel drive, you'll experience a smooth ride every time you hit the gas pedal. The Camry's independent suspension ensures optimal handling, while the compact spare tire gives you peace of mind on any journey. Whether you're cruising during the day or driving at night, the halogen headlamps with auto on/off provide excellent visibility.Inside the Camry, you'll find comfortable front bucket seats with adjustable features for the perfect fit. The center console armrest offers extra storage space for your essentials, and the tilt/telescoping steering wheel includes convenient audio controls. Plus, with the tire pressure monitor system and maintenance indicator, you can easily keep track of your car's health.Safety is a top priority in the Camry, with advanced airbags, side curtain airbags, and a driver knee airbag all in place to protect you and your passengers. Additionally, the LATCH child restraint system ensures that young ones are secure on the go. Best of all, a Carfax report is available for this Camry, giving you added confidence in your purchase. Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this reliable and stylish ride!

Experience the power and sophistication of the 2007 Chevrolet Impala SS. This striking silver sedan boasts a commanding 5.3L V8 engine, delivering an exhilarating 18 city/27 highway MPG. Beneath its sleek exterior lies a wealth of premium features that elevate the driving experience.

• Sunroof with power sunshade
• Bose premium 8-speaker audio system
• 18" polished aluminum wheels
• Convenience package with universal home remote, auto-dimming rearview mirror, and heated power-adjustable mirrors

Stepping inside, you'll be greeted by the Impala SS's luxurious Preferred Equipment Group 1SS package, which includes:

• Leather-wrapped steering wheel with audio controls
• Heated front seats
• 4-wheel antilock disc brakes
• Power sunroof with sunshade

The Impala SS's impressive list of features continues with dual-zone climate control, OnStar emergency communication system, and a host of advanced safety technologies. With its striking good looks, powerful performance, and exceptional amenities, this Impala SS is sure to elevate your driving experience.

Imagine the confidence and comfort you'll feel behind the wheel of this exceptional Chevrolet. Whether you're commuting to the office or embarking on a weekend getaway, the Impala SS will deliver a driving experience that is both thrilling and refined.

We understand that purchasing a vehicle is a significant decision, and we're here to guide you through the process. Our knowledgeable sales team is dedicated to ensuring you find the perfect car to meet your needs and exceed your expectations. We invite you to visit our showroom and experience the Impala SS for yourself. Let us demonstrate how this exceptional sedan can enhance your driving pleasure and elevate your lifestyle.

This 2007 Chevrolet Impala SS is now available for $8,990. Don't miss the opportunity to own this remarkable vehicle. Contact us today to schedule a test drive and discover the true meaning of driving enjoyment.

Vehicle Details
Discover exceptional value in Corinth, MS with this 2018 Nissan Altima 2.5 S — a reliable, fuel-efficient sedan that fits your daily needs and budget. Powered by a smooth 4-cylinder 2.5L gasoline engine and front-wheel drive, this Nissan Altima delivers confident handling, comfortable highway cruising, and impressive fuel economy for commuters and families alike. This well-maintained example comes loaded with practical tech and safety features: Hands Free Bluetooth for effortless calling and music streaming, Forward Collision Warning to help keep you and your passengers safer on the road, and a Back-Up Camera to make parking and reversing easier in tight spots. Step inside to a comfortable, thoughtfully designed cabin with roomy seating and intuitive controls, built for long drives and busy schedules. The 2018 Nissan Altima 2.5 S blends modern convenience with proven Nissan reliability, offering a smooth ride and predictable maintenance costs. Located in Corinth, MS, this vehicle is being offered at the best price in the area — an unbeatable combination of quality and affordability. If you want a dependable sedan with the safety tech and everyday comfort you need, this Nissan Altima is ready to go. Contact us today to arrange a test drive in Corinth, MS and see why this 2018 Nissan Altima 2.5 S is the smart choice for value-conscious buyers seeking performance, safety, and comfort. Act fast — deals like this go quickly.

Equipment
Bluetooth technology is built into this 2018 Nissan Altima , keeping your hands on the steering wheel and your focus on the road. This vehicle's Forward Collision Warning system alerts the driver to potential front-end collisions, enhancing safety. See what's behind you with the back up camera on the Nissan Altima. This Nissan Altima has a 4 Cyl, 2.5L high output engine. Front wheel drive on it gives you better traction and better fuel economy. This Nissan Altima shines with clean polished lines coated with an elegant white finish. Maintaining a stable interior temperature in the vehicle is easy with the climate control system. The high efficiency automatic transmission shifts smoothly and allows you to relax while driving. Enjoy the tried and true gasoline engine in this Nissan Altima. This 2018 Nissan Altima features cruise control for long trips. Anti-lock brakes will help you stop in an emergency. The Electronic Stability Control will keep you on your intended path.

CARFAX One-Owner, Clean CARFAX, and Ford Blue Advantage Blue Certified, this Magnetic 2018 Ford Fiesta SE FWD is a smart and fuel-efficient compact car that’s perfect for daily commuting and city driving. Powered by a responsive 1.6L I4 Ti-VCT engine paired with a 6-speed automatic transmission, the Fiesta delivers smooth performance while achieving an excellent 27 MPG city and 37 MPG highway. Its compact size makes it easy to maneuver and park, while still offering a comfortable ride and practical interior space. This Fiesta is a recent arrival and represents an outstanding value for budget-minded shoppers.

As a Ford Blue Advantage Blue Certified vehicle, it has completed a comprehensive 139-point inspection and includes a transferable warranty, vehicle history report, roadside assistance, and a $100 warranty deductible. Certification coverage also provides a 3-month/4,000-mile limited warranty (whichever comes first) beginning after the original new vehicle warranty expires or from the certified purchase date, along with 11,000 FordPass Rewards Points to use toward your first maintenance visit. This model has earned industry recognition including 2018 KBB.com Brand Image Awards and 2018 KBB.com 10 Most Awarded Brands, highlighting Ford’s reputation for quality and value. Price includes a $500 Dealer Finance Discount and $500 Trade-In Assistance Discount. Tax, tag, title, doc fee of $699, and electronic filing fee of $190.98 are additional and not included in the sale price.

Get ready to turn heads in this **2018 Ford Fusion SE** finished in sleek **Magnetic** and powered by the efficient yet responsive **1.5L EcoBoost engine** with **FWD**—a perfect blend of style, performance, and everyday practicality!

Inside, this Fusion SE is packed with comfort and technology you’ll appreciate every drive. The **Cloth/Vinyl Bolster Seats** and **Leather-Wrapped Steering Wheel** give the cabin a refined feel, while **Dual-Zone Electronic Automatic Temperature Control** keeps both driver and passengers comfortable year-round. The **SE Appearance Package** adds sporty touches like **18” Magnetic-Painted Aluminum Wheels** and a **Rear Spoiler**, giving this sedan a bold, modern look.

Stay connected and entertained with the **SYNC 3 Communications & Entertainment System**, **SiriusXM Radio**, and **AM/FM/MP3/Single-CD audio system**, making every commute or road trip more enjoyable. Convenience features like **Remote Keyless Entry**, **Fully Automatic Headlights**, **Delay-Off Headlights**, and **Halogen Fog Lamps** ensure ease of use and added confidence in changing conditions.

Safety and efficiency go hand in hand with this Fusion, delivering an impressive **23 MPG city/34 MPG highway**, making it a smart choice for both daily driving and long-distance travel.

Even better, this vehicle’s **odometer is 29,114 miles below market average**, making it an outstanding value that won’t last long. A well-equipped, low-mileage Fusion like this is hard to find—especially at this price point.

👉 **Call or stop by Gilland Ford today!** Don’t miss your chance to own this sharp, fuel-efficient 2018 Ford Fusion SE before it’s gone!

description:
Turn heads on the Emerald Coast in this Recent Arrival 2018 Ford Fusion SE FWD, now available at Toyota of Fort Walton Beach. Finished in eye-catching Lightning Blue, this stylish and fuel-efficient sedan is powered by a responsive 1.5L EcoBoost engine paired with a smooth 6-speed automatic transmission, delivering an impressive 23 MPG city/34 MPG highway. Even better, this Fusion has 42,023 miles below market average, making it an outstanding value for drivers seeking a low-mileage used sedan in Northwest Florida.

This Fusion is well equipped with the desirable Equipment Group 201A, SE Appearance Package, and SE Technology Package, combining sporty design with everyday comfort and modern connectivity. The Appearance Package adds cloth/vinyl bolstered sport seats, a sleek rear spoiler, and bold 18-inch magnetic-painted aluminum wheels, giving this Fusion a more aggressive and refined look. Inside, the Technology Package upgrades your driving experience with dual-zone electronic automatic climate control and the intuitive SYNC 3 Communications & Entertainment System.

The thoughtfully designed cabin features power driver and passenger seats, steering-wheel-mounted audio controls, SiriusXM radio, and a voice-activated touchscreen navigation system. With the rearview camera, fully automatic headlights, and illuminated entry, this Fusion delivers the convenience todays drivers expect from a modern midsize sedan.

Safety comes standard with electronic stability control, traction control, brake assist, four-wheel disc brakes, Ford 911 Assist, and a comprehensive airbag systemhelping provide confidence and peace of mind on every drive. The independent suspension and composed ride quality make this Fusion equally at home on daily commutes, road trips, or cruising the beaches of Fort Walton and Destin.

At Toyota of Fort Walton Beach, you can purchase with confidence. We research the local market within a 500-mile radius to ensure our vehicles are competitively priced based on real market data, vehicle history, and overall condition. After your test drive, ask your product specialist for a full research market analysis. If you find a comparable vehicle for less, were happy to review it and either match the price or show you what makes ours the better value.

If youre searching for a used Ford Fusion for sale in Fort Walton Beach, a fuel-efficient sedan near Destin, or a low-mileage midsize car on the Emerald Coast, this 2018 Ford Fusion SE is a smart and stylish choice.

description:
Turn heads and enjoy every drive in this **2018 Mazda Mazda3 Touring**, finished in stunning **Snowflake White Pearl** and powered by Mazda’s responsive **SKYACTIV® 2.5L 4-Cylinder engine** with **front-wheel drive**—a perfect blend of sporty performance and everyday efficiency.

Step inside and you’ll find a thoughtfully designed cabin packed with comfort and technology. **Front bucket seats with heating** keep you comfortable year-round, while the intuitive **MAZDA CONNECT™ Infotainment System with voice command** keeps navigation, music, and communication right at your fingertips. Enjoy your favorite stations with the **AM/FM/HD Audio System**, and let the sunshine in with the **power sliding-glass moonroof featuring an interior sunshade**—perfect for open-road cruising.

Convenience comes standard with **remote keyless entry**, making daily errands and commutes effortless. Mazda’s attention to safety and quality shines through, and this vehicle is backed by a **Clean CARFAX**, giving you added peace of mind and confidence in your purchase.

Priced to move and offering exceptional value for a well-equipped, reliable compact sedan, this Mazda3 Touring **won’t last long** on our lot.

👉 **Call or stop by Gilland Ford today** to take it for a test drive and see why this Mazda3 is such a smart buy!

Powered by a fuel-efficient Nu 2.0L I4 engine paired with a smooth 6-speed shiftable automatic transmission, this Forte delivers both performance and economy. Enjoy convenience features like Bluetooth wireless connectivity for hands-free calls and audio streaming, SiriusXM Satellite Radio, USB and auxiliary audio input, and steering wheel-mounted controls for audio and cruise. The Forte's sleek design is complemented by body-color bumpers and mirrors, full wheel covers, and rear solar-tinted glass. Well-maintained and ready for its next owner, this sedan is perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways.

description:
Welcome to Keith Mccoy Automive!At Keith Mccoy, we are primarily a wholesaler providing top-quality used vehicles to franchise and independent dealers. However, we also cater to retail customers looking for great deals on reliable vehicles. If you're a retail customer interested in purchasing from us for a great price, give us a call at 214-230-2300 for more details on how you can buy from us!We acquire our inventory from three different sources: local franchise dealer trade-ins, purchases from individual car owners, and auto auctions statewide. To guarantee the highest quality for all our customers, every vehicle goes through three rigorous layers of inspection:
  • Initial Inspection: Upon arrival, our certified technicians conduct a thorough inspection covering suspension, electric, and mechanical components. They provide detailed notes and recommendations on areas requiring repair.
  • Third-Party Review: Next, the vehicles are taken to certified mechanic shops, where a 27-point inspection is performed. All necessary repairs are completed to ensure the vehicle is safe and reliable.
  • State Inspection: Finally, each vehicle undergoes a state inspection to confirm it is roadworthy and meets all safety standards for highway use.
    • To guarantee the best pricing and thousands in savings for all our retail customers, we offer a guaranteed price match within the DFW metroplex. If you find a vehicle with a similar year, trim, Carfax history, and comparable mileage available at another used car dealership in the area, we guarantee to match their price.Whether you're a dealer or a retail customer, we re here to ensure you receive the highest quality product. description:
Discover the perfect balance of style, performance, and technology in this stunning 2018 Honda Accord EX. With its sleek black exterior and a host of premium features, this Accord is poised to elevate your driving experience.

• Power driver seat
• Power moonroof
• Heated door mirrors
• Apple CarPlay/Android Auto
• Heated front seats

Slip into the driver's seat and experience the smooth power of the 1.5T I4 DOHC 16V Turbocharged VTEC engine, paired with a seamless CVT transmission. Enjoy exceptional fuel efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 30 city/38 highway MPG, allowing you to go farther on every tank.

The Accord EX is more than just a practical sedan – it's a testament to Honda's commitment to innovation. Indulge in the convenience of the 180-Watt AM/FM/HD/SiriusXM Audio System, complete with 8 speakers and steering wheel-mounted audio controls. Stay connected with the HondaLink emergency communication system, and let the Blind Spot Information (BSI) System guide you with confidence.

Elevate your driving experience with the Accord EX's impressive array of advanced safety features. Enjoy the peace of mind of ABS brakes, Electronic Stability Control, and a suite of airbags, including a driver's knee airbag. The Rear Camera and Auto High-Beam Headlights further enhance your visibility and control on the road.

This Accord EX is priced below market value, making it an exceptional value proposition. With a sleek black exterior and a well-appointed interior, this vehicle is sure to turn heads and impress. Don't miss your chance to make this Accord EX your own – schedule a test drive today and experience the difference for yourself.

description: Conquer Every Terrain with the 2025 Toyota Tundra Hybrid TRD Pro: Where Power Meets Efficiency in a Midnight Black Metallic Masterpiece Experience the perfect blend of power and efficiency with the 2025 Toyota Tundra Hybrid TRD Pro. This used gem, dressed in an alluring Midnight Black Metallic, is engineered for those who crave adventure without compromising on sustainability. At its heart, a robust 3.4L V6 engine paired with a gas/electric hybrid system delivers impressive performance, while the 10-speed automatic transmission ensures smooth and responsive handling. The Tundra Hybrid TRD Pro is equipped with advanced safety features like Blind Spot Monitor, Lane Departure Warning, and Front Collision Mitigation, offering peace of mind on every journey. Its rugged 4D Crewmax body style and all-terrain tires are ready to tackle any landscape, while the panoramic roof invites the great outdoors inside. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort and technology, featuring heated and cooled front seats with adjustable lumbar support, a premium sound system, and a state-of-the-art navigation system. The smart device integration and WiFi hotspot keep you connected, while the adaptive cruise control and aerial view display system enhance driving pleasure. Discover the ultimate driving experience with the Toyota Tundra Hybrid TRD Pro. Be sure to call or visit Vandergriff Toyota to discover more. Your new favorite vehicle awaits - don't let someone else drive it home!

description:
Experience the Sophisticated Style and Impressive Performance of the 2018 Kia Optima EX

This stunning 2018 Kia Optima EX is the perfect blend of modern elegance and dynamic capability, making it an exceptional choice for the discerning driver. With its sleek exterior design, meticulously crafted interior, and a wealth of advanced features, this Optima EX is poised to exceed your expectations and elevate your driving experience.

Key features include:
• Backup Camera
• Bluetooth
• Panoramic Sunroof
• Heated & Ventilated Front Seats
• 10-Way Power Adjustable Passenger Seat
• Auto Dimming Rear View Mirror with HomeLink & Compass

Powered by a 2.4L I4 DGI DOHC engine mated to a 6-Speed Automatic with Sportmatic transmission, this Optima EX delivers an impressive balance of efficiency and performance, with an EPA-estimated 24 MPG in the city and 34 MPG on the highway.

Step inside the Optima EX and you'll be greeted by a beautifully appointed cabin that exudes refinement. The leather-wrapped steering wheel and shift knob provide a premium feel, while the heated and ventilated front seats ensure your comfort in any weather. The panoramic sunroof floods the interior with natural light, creating an airy and spacious atmosphere.

The advanced technology features of the Optima EX are designed to enhance your driving experience. The intuitive infotainment system with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration keeps you connected and entertained, while the rear-view camera and parking sensors provide added confidence and convenience when maneuvering in tight spaces.

Safety is also a top priority in the Optima EX, with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies, including forward collision warning, automatic emergency braking, and lane departure warning, helping to keep you and your passengers secure on the road.

This meticulously maintained 2018 Kia Optima EX, with just 106,062 miles, represents an exceptional value in the pre-owned market. Experience the sophistication and performance of this remarkable vehicle for yourself. We invite you to schedule a test drive and discover the joy of driving the Optima EX.

Elevate your driving experience with this exceptional 2018 Nissan Sentra S. This sleek and efficient sedan boasts a striking Gray exterior, complemented by a well-appointed interior that caters to your every need.

• Carpeted Floor Mats w/Trunk Mat
• Air Conditioning
• Rear window defroster

Powered by a 1.8L 4-Cylinder DOHC 16V engine paired with a CVT with Xtronic transmission, this Sentra S delivers an impressive fuel economy of 27 city MPG and 35 highway MPG, making it the perfect companion for your daily commute or weekend adventures.

Beyond its exceptional performance, this Sentra S is equipped with a host of features that prioritize your comfort and convenience. Enjoy the seamless integration of the AM/FM/CD Aux-In Audio System, complete with steering wheel-mounted audio controls, and stay connected with the remote keyless entry system.

Safety is also a top priority, with the Sentra S boasting a comprehensive array of advanced safety features, including ABS brakes, dual front impact airbags, dual front side impact airbags, and Electronic Stability Control. You can drive with confidence, knowing that your well-being is protected.

Whether you're seeking a reliable and efficient daily driver or a versatile family sedan, this 2018 Nissan Sentra S is poised to exceed your expectations. Experience the perfect balance of style, performance, and technology by scheduling a V.I.P. appointment at Castle Rock Ford today.

Sleek, Smart, and Highly Efficient: The 2018 Chevrolet Malibu LT
Upgrade your daily drive without emptying your wallet at the pump!
This 2018 Chevy Malibu LT is the perfect blend of eye-catching design, comfortable features, and modern technology. As the popular mid-level trim, it delivers everything you need in a sedan—and much more.
The Intelligent Choice for Commuters
- Exceptional Fuel Economy: Powered by the responsive 1.5L Turbo 4-Cylinder engine, you'll enjoy an outstanding EPA-estimated 36 MPG Highway (27 MPG City), making your commute—and every road trip—more affordable.
- Modern Connectivity: Stay connected and entertained with the excellent Chevrolet MyLink Infotainment System featuring a touchscreen display, Apple CarPlay®, and Android Auto™ compatibility.
- Built-in Wi-Fi: Features OnStar 4G LTE with a built-in Wi-Fi® Hotspot (subscription required) to keep you and your passengers connected on the go.
- Comfort & Convenience: The LT trim adds key features like LED Daytime Running Lights, Heated Side Mirrors, an 8-way power driver seat, and SiriusXM Satellite Radio capability.
Style That Stands Out
Forget the boring sedan. The Malibu boasts a sleek, sculpted profile and a roomy, well-designed interior that gives you and your passengers plenty of space.
- Engine: 1.5L Turbo I-4
- Transmission: 6-Speed Automatic
- Seating: 5
- Features: Power Driver's Seat, Rear Vision Camera, Steering Wheel Controls, and more!

description:
Discover the perfect blend of style, efficiency, and convenience in this 2018 Toyota Yaris iA Base. With its sleek blue exterior and well-appointed interior, this compact sedan offers an exceptional driving experience that will captivate your senses.

• Backup Camera
• Bluetooth

This Yaris iA is equipped with a host of features that cater to your every need, including air conditioning, power windows, and remote keyless entry. The 7-inch touchscreen display audio system with AM/FM radio ensures you'll enjoy your favorite tunes on the go.

Certified as part of our Dealin Doug Certified Advantage Pre-Owned Program, this Yaris iA has undergone a rigorous inspection and reconditioning process to ensure it meets the highest standards of quality and reliability. You can drive with confidence, knowing that this vehicle is backed by either a 12-Month/12,000-Mile or a 3-Year/100,000-Mile Limited Powertrain Warranty, along with 24/7 emergency roadside assistance.

Powered by a 1.5L DOHC engine paired with a 6-speed transmission, the Yaris iA delivers an exceptional blend of performance and efficiency. Whether navigating busy city streets or cruising down the highway, this compact sedan will provide a smooth and responsive driving experience.

The Yaris iA's impressive list of safety features, including ABS brakes, dual front impact airbags, and electronic stability control, will give you peace of mind on every journey. The rear-view camera and traction control further enhance your confidence behind the wheel.

Step inside the Yaris iA and discover the comfort and convenience of the split-folding rear seats, tilt and telescoping steering wheel, and driver's vanity mirror. The 16-inch alloy wheels and body-color bumpers add a touch of style to this practical and well-equipped vehicle.

Certification Program Details: Dealin Doug Certified Advantage Pre-Owned Vehicle offers either a 12 Month/12,000 Mile or a 3 Year/100,000 mile Limited Powertrain Warranty. Our 12 Month Certification begins on the vehicle purchase date and continues up to 12 months or 12,000 miles in addition to the odometer at time of purchase. Or, our 3 Year/100,000 mile certification continues up to 3 years from the purchase date or when 100,000 miles is reached on the odometer, whichever occurs first. Our 3 Year 100,000 certification Includes 24/7 emergency roadside assistance. Please ask for details, restrictions may apply.

With its exceptional value, impressive features, and certified pre-owned status, this 2018 Toyota Yaris iA Base is the perfect choice for the savvy buyer seeking a reliable and well-equipped compact sedan. Visit our showroom today to experience the Yaris iA for yourself and discover why it's the smart choice for your next vehicle.

Pre-Owned 2018 Nissan Maxima Platinum

The 2018 Nissan Maxima Platinum delivers bold performance, upscale comfort, and advanced technology making it an excellent choice for drivers who want the excitement of a sport sedan with the refinement and features of a luxury vehicle.

Key Highlights:

Strong & Smooth Performance:

3.5-liter V6 engine delivering impressive power and responsive acceleration

Continuously Variable Transmission (CVT) designed for smooth, confident driving

Sport-tuned suspension providing a balanced and engaging ride

Platinum Interior Comfort:

Premium leather-appointed seating with a refined, modern cabin design

Heated and ventilated front seats, heated rear seats, and a heated steering wheel

Power-adjustable front seats with memory and dual-zone automatic climate control

Spacious seating for five with a generously sized trunk

Advanced Technology:

Touchscreen infotainment system with navigation

Premium Bose audio system for an immersive listening experience

Intelligent Key with push-button start

Around View Monitor offering a 360-degree camera view for easier parking

Safety & Driver Assist:

Automatic Emergency Braking

Blind Spot Warning and Rear Cross Traffic Alert

Lane Departure Warning

Vehicle Dynamic Control and Traction Control for confident handling in changing road conditions

Sporty & Sophisticated Design:

Aggressive exterior styling with signature Maxima design cues

Low, wide stance giving the sedan a commanding road presence

A strong blend of performance, luxury, and everyday usability

All pre-owned vehicles include our complimentary 3-month/3,000-mile limited powertrain warranty for added peace of mind.

Call (303) 776-0443 or stop by Valley Nissan Mitsubishi, 1005 Ken Pratt Blvd, Longmont, CO 80501, to experience the power and refinement of this Nissan Maxima Platinum for yourself.

PRESTIGE PACKAGE, NANO GRAY METALLIC, BLACK, LEATHER SEATING SURFACES, SPORT PACKAGE, SPORT SUSPENSION This A3 Sedan has the following features: Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Lane departure prevention - Keep it between the lines. It only takes a moment of inattention for your vehicle to drift. With lane departure prevention, your vehicle takes corrective action to help you avoid unintentionally moving out of your lane. Lane departure prevention is an extra level of safety for you and those around you.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.

Discover the perfect blend of style, performance, and convenience in this stunning 2018 Volkswagen Jetta 1.8T SE Sport. With its sleek black exterior, this Jetta exudes a bold and sophisticated presence that is sure to turn heads wherever you go.

Elevate your driving experience with a host of premium features, including:

• MONSTER MATS W/LOGO RUBBER MAT KIT (SET OF 4)
• Heavy Duty Trunk Liner w/VW CarGo Blocks
• CHROME EXHAUST TIPS (Set of 2)

Slip behind the wheel and enjoy the responsive power of the 1.8L TSI engine, paired with a smooth-shifting 6-Speed Automatic with Tiptronic transmission. With an impressive 24 city/33 highway MPG, this Jetta delivers exceptional fuel efficiency, allowing you to spend more time on the open road and less at the pump.

The Jetta's well-appointed interior features a host of cutting-edge technology, including a 6.3" touchscreen infotainment system, SiriusXM radio, and a rearview camera for added convenience and safety. Sink into the comfortable, heated V-Tex Leatherette seats and let the power moonroof fill the cabin with natural light, creating a truly premium driving experience.

Safety is paramount, and this Jetta is equipped with a suite of advanced driver-assistance features, including ABS brakes, Electronic Stability Control, and a comprehensive airbag system to keep you and your passengers secure on the road.

Whether you're commuting to the office, embarking on a weekend getaway, or simply enjoying the thrill of the open road, this 2018 Volkswagen Jetta 1.8T SE Sport is the perfect companion. Experience the joy of driving with this exceptional vehicle, and let it elevate your daily commute to new heights.

We invite you to visit our showroom and take this Jetta for a test drive. Our knowledgeable sales team is here to answer any questions you may have and help you discover why this Jetta is the perfect fit for your lifestyle. Don't miss your chance to make this stunning Jetta your own - schedule your test drive today.

Rest assured, you and your loved ones will be well-protected on every journey.With its impressive fuel efficiency, advanced technology, and robust safety features, this 2018 Subaru Impreza 2.0i is a standout in its class. Now, with Distance pacing cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and the vehicle ahead. Distance pacing cruise control, your ultimate co-pilot.
Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Lane departure prevention - Keep it between the lines. It only takes a moment of inattention for your vehicle to drift. With lane departure prevention, your vehicle takes corrective action to help you avoid unintentionally moving out of your lane. Lane departure prevention is an extra level of safety for you and those around you.

2018 Honda Civic LX - Clean, Reliable, Award-Winning Value!

Start the new year with proven reliability and everyday efficiency in this 2018 Honda Civic LX. Known for its long-term dependability, smooth ride, and excellent fuel economy, the Civic continues to be one of the most trusted compact sedans on the roadmaking it a smart choice for commuting, first-time buyers, or anyone looking for worry-free ownership.

This Civic features a clean black cloth interior, hands-free Bluetooth connectivity, and a back-up camera to make daily driving easier and more convenient.   • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
In-car Entertainment
  • Touchscreen - flat out convenient. Say goodbye to the twists and turns of your daily drive...we're talking about buttons and knobs of course! Touchscreen allows you to control certain features with your fingertips, making it easy to use while also providing information at a glance. With touchscreen, your fingerprints will be all over your drive.
Safety and Security
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.

  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Rear collision mitigation - It has your back. Rear collision mitigation uses sensors to monitor the area behind you. description:
Experience the perfect blend of efficiency and style with the 2018 Honda Clarity Plug-In Hybrid, the ultimate combination of eco-friendly technology and modern design. Its sleek Modern Steel Metallic exterior turns heads, while the advanced 4 Cylinder Engine paired with a seamless CVT provides a smooth and efficient ride. With the reliability of a front-wheel drive system, this sedan effortlessly delivers performance and practicality in every drive. CarFax One Owner! Popular Options and Features Include: Convenience
  • Distance pacing cruise control with traffic stop-go. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with Distance pacing cruise control with traffic stop-go, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and the vehicle ahead. It's stop/go feature automatically brings the vehicle to a stop if traffic stops and resumes distance pacing cruise when traffic starts to move again. Distance pacing cruise control with traffic stop-go, your ultimate co-pilot.
Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Lane departure prevention - Keep it between the lines. It only takes a moment of inattention for your vehicle to drift. With lane departure prevention, your vehicle takes corrective action to help you avoid unintentionally moving out of your lane. Lane departure prevention is an extra level of safety for you and those around you.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
About Dublin Honda Not only are we Honda enthusiasts at Dublin Honda, we're dedicated members of the local community. Ken Harvey opened Dublin Honda in 1977 and has helped literally thousands upon thousands of Happy Honda Owners find and maintain their Hondas. To this day, Dublin Honda remains a family-owned and family-operated dealership, committed to the local community we serve and in which we live.

Discover the perfect balance of style, efficiency, and technology in this 2018 Ford Focus SE. With its sleek black exterior and a host of impressive features, this compact car is ready to elevate your driving experience.

• 6-Speed Automatic (PowerShift) (Does Not Include SelectShift)
• Daytime Running Lamps

Boasting an EPA-estimated 26 city/38 highway MPG, this Focus SE delivers exceptional fuel efficiency to help you save at the pump. Under the hood, the 2.0L I4 DGI Ti-VCT engine provides responsive performance, seamlessly paired with the 6-speed automatic transmission.

Step inside and you'll be greeted by a well-appointed interior, featuring cloth front bucket seats, a front center armrest, and a split-folding rear seat for versatile cargo-carrying capabilities. The SYNC Communications & Entertainment System keeps you connected, while the steering wheel-mounted audio controls and tilt/telescoping steering wheel provide added convenience.

Safety is also a top priority, with features like dual front impact airbags, dual front side impact airbags, an emergency communication system, and electronic stability control to give you peace of mind on the road.

Alloy wheels and a rear parking camera add a touch of style and practicality, enhancing both the aesthetic and functional aspects of this Focus SE.

Whether you're commuting to work, running errands, or embarking on a weekend getaway, this 2018 Ford Focus SE is the perfect companion. With its impressive combination of efficiency, technology, and safety, it's a smart choice for discerning drivers like you.

Experience the joy of driving with this exceptional 2018 Ford Focus SE. Visit our showroom today to take it for a test drive and discover how this compact car can elevate your daily commute. We're confident you'll be impressed by its exceptional value and capabilities.

description: Meet this 2018 Hyundai Elantra Value Edition in eye-catching Lakeside Blue with a clean Gray cloth interior — a smart, economical compact sedan that balances comfort, safety, and everyday usability. Performance & Efficiency - Powered by Hyundai’s Nu 2.0L inline-4 engine producing 147 hp and 132 lb-ft of torque, paired with a smooth 6-speed automatic transmission for confident city driving and relaxed highway cruising. - Excellent fuel economy: EPA-rated at 28 MPG city and 37 MPG highway, making it an outstanding choice for commuters and road-trippers alike. - This particular Elantra has under 58,000 miles on the odometer, averaging less than 7,000 miles per year — a low-mileage example that’s been gently used. Comfort & Convenience (factory-equipped) - Comfortable Gray cloth seats with supportive front buckets and a 60/40 split-folding rear seat to expand cargo flexibility when needed. - Manual seat adjustments plus ample front and rear legroom for passengers, well-suited for daily driving and longer trips. - Dual-zone automatic climate control or single-zone automatic climate control (factory comfort package dependent) keeps the cabin comfortable on any drive. - Power windows and door locks, remote keyless entry, and cruise control for relaxed highway driving. - Tilt-and-telescoping steering wheel with integrated audio and Bluetooth controls for hands-on convenience. Technology & Infotainment - A user-friendly infotainment system with touchscreen display, Bluetooth hands-free phone and audio streaming, and USB/AUX inputs for smartphone and media connectivity. - Apple CarPlay and Android Auto compatibility (standard on many 2018 Elantra Value Editions) for seamless navigation, calls, and music. - Steering wheel-mounted audio controls and a multi-function trip computer for easy access to vehicle info. Safety & Driver Aids (factory-standard) - A comprehensive airbag system including front, side, and curtain airbags for occupant protection. - Standard safety systems such as ABS brakes, electronic stability control (ESC), traction control, and a tire pressure monitoring system. - Rearview backup camera for safer reversing and parking awareness. - Strong crashworthiness design with crumple zones and reinforced occupant cell — Hyundai’s attention to safety is built into the platform. Exterior & Practical Details - Striking Lakeside Blue exterior paint that stands out in the parking lot. - Clean, aerodynamic profile with body-colored mirrors and handles, factory alloy wheels complete the look. - Halogen headlights with daytime running lights for visibility and a modern appearance. - Generous trunk space for a compact sedan and split-folding rear seats to accommodate longer items. Why this Elantra? If you’re looking for a dependable, fuel-efficient compact sedan with low miles, solid safety equipment, and a comfortable interior, this 2018 Hyundai Elantra Value Edition is a great fit. The Lakeside Blue exterior and Gray interior are a timeless combination, and the well-balanced 2.0L engine delivers a pleasant mix of economy and everyday performance. Ready to see it in person or take a test drive? It’s an easy choice for buyers who want proven reliability, comfort, and efficiency.

description: Titan Black, Perforated V-Tex Leatherette Seating Surfaces, Urano Gray. The 2018 Volkswagen Passat R-Line Auto is a captivating sedan that seamlessly blends performance and style. It boasts a robust 2.0L 4-cylinder engine that ensures an invigorating drive, offering a balance of power and efficiency that is perfect for both daily commutes and weekend adventures. The R-Line styling adds a sporty touch, characterized by its distinctive front and rear bumpers, a striking black grille, and stylish side skirts that enhance its aerodynamic profile. Inside, the Passat R-Line Auto is designed with comfort and technology at the forefront. The spacious interior provides ample legroom for both front and rear passengers, ensuring a comfortable journey for all. Premium materials, an intuitive infotainment system with a touchscreen interface, and integrated smartphone connectivity contribute to a superior driving experience. The vehicle's advanced safety features include a rearview camera, adaptive cruise control, and blind-spot monitoring, offering peace of mind on every journey. Moreover, this is a Carfax 1-Owner vehicle, signifying that it has been meticulously maintained with a well-documented service history, ensuring reliability and longevity. The Passat's stylish alloy wheels and available sunroof further elevate its appeal, making it an ideal choice for discerning drivers. With a combined focus on performance, luxury, and safety, the 2018 Volkswagen Passat R-Line Auto stands out as an exceptional choice in the midsize sedan market, ready to meet the demands of any driver with confidence and grace. Discover the perfect blend of style, technology, and performance with this 2022 Hyundai Kona SEL. This stunning SUV offers a captivating exterior design, a wealth of advanced features, and the confidence of all-wheel drive, making it the ideal choice for the discerning driver.

Highlighted by its sleek Silver exterior, the Kona SEL boasts a range of premium amenities that elevate the driving experience. Key features include:

• Apple CarPlay and Android Auto
• Wireless device charging
• Power sunroof
• Blind spot assist
• Rear backup camera
• Heated front seats
• Leather-wrapped steering wheel and shift knob
• Automatic temperature control
• NFC digital key

The Kona's impressive 2.0L I4 engine and CVT transmission deliver a smooth, responsive ride, while the available all-wheel drive system ensures confident handling in all conditions. With an EPA-estimated 28 city and 33 highway MPG, this SUV strikes the perfect balance between power and efficiency.

Beyond its impressive performance, the Kona SEL also prioritizes your safety and convenience. The comprehensive Convenience Package includes a host of advanced technologies, such as a power tilt-and-slide sunroof, wireless device charging, and a hidden cargo-area storage compartment for effortless organization.

With its sleek styling, cutting-edge features, and impressive capabilities, this 2022 Hyundai Kona SEL is the perfect companion for your next adventure. Experience the difference for yourself by scheduling a test drive today. We're confident you'll be impressed by the Kona's exceptional value and the unparalleled customer service that has made our dealership a trusted part of the Sarasota community for over 30 years.
