description:
Introducing the luxurious and powerful 2018 Mercedes-Benz CLA CLA 250! This stunning vehicle combines style, comfort, and performance, making it the perfect choice for those who demand the best.

With its sleek and aerodynamic design, the CLA CLA 250 exudes elegance and sophistication. The spacious interior is adorned with premium materials, providing a comfortable and lavish driving experience. Plus, with ample legroom and cargo space, you can bring all your essentials along for the ride.

Under the hood, the CLA CLA 250 boasts a powerful 2.0-liter turbocharged engine, delivering an impressive 208 horsepower. Paired with a 7-speed dual-clutch transmission, this vehicle offers smooth and responsive handling. And with advanced safety features such as blind spot assist and lane keeping assist, you can feel confident and secure on the road.

description:
Discover the perfect blend of style, comfort, and reliability in this 2018 Toyota Camry L. This exceptional sedan offers an unparalleled driving experience, packed with a host of impressive features that cater to your every need.

Boasting a sleek and modern exterior in a stunning White color, this Camry L exudes a sense of sophistication and timeless appeal. Under the hood, the powerful 2.5L I4 DOHC 16V engine, paired with an 8-Speed Automatic transmission, delivers an impressive performance, with an exceptional fuel efficiency of 29 city/41 highway MPG.

Key features that set this Camry apart:

• 6 Speakers
• AM/FM radio
• Radio data system
• Radio: Entune 3.0 Audio
• Air Conditioning
• Rear window defroster
• Power steering
• Power windows
• Remote keyless entry
• Steering wheel mounted audio controls
• Four wheel independent suspension
• Speed-sensing steering
• Traction control
• 4-Wheel Disc Brakes
• ABS brakes
• Dual front impact airbags
• Dual front side impact airbags
• Knee airbag
• Low tire pressure warning
• Occupant sensing airbag
• Overhead airbag
• Rear anti-roll bar
• Rear side impact airbag
• Brake assist
• Electronic Stability Control
• Exterior Parking Camera Rear
• Auto High-beam Headlights
• Delay-off headlights
• Fully automatic headlights
• Panic alarm
• Speed control

Step inside this Camry L and experience the epitome of comfort and convenience. The spacious interior, with its Fabric Seat Trim and Front Bucket Seats, provides a relaxing and supportive environment for you and your passengers. The Front Center Armrest and Telescoping steering wheel ensure a personalized and ergonomic driving experience, while the Tilt steering wheel and Trip computer keep you informed and in control.

This 2018 Toyota Camry L is a true testament to the brand's renowned reliability and quality. With a list price of $14,500, it represents an exceptional value proposition, making it the perfect choice for the discerning buyer seeking a reliable, feature-rich, and stylish sedan.

Don't miss the opportunity to experience the exceptional driving dynamics and unparalleled comfort of this 2018 Toyota Camry L. Visit our showroom today and let us guide you through the details of this remarkable vehicle. We're confident that once you take it for a test drive, you'll be convinced that this Camry is the perfect fit for your lifestyle.

Introducing the 2018 Ford Taurus SE, a sleek and powerful sedan that will take your driving experience to the next level. With its 3.5L V6 engine, delivering a whopping 288 horsepower and 254 ft. lbs. of torque, this car is ready to hit the road with a roar. And with a 6-speed shiftable automatic transmission, you can effortlessly switch between gears for a smooth and responsive ride.

But the 2018 Ford Taurus SE offers more than just impressive performance. Step inside and you'll be greeted with a spacious and comfortable interior, perfect for long drives and daily commutes. The seats are designed with premium materials and extra cushioning, ensuring a luxurious and comfortable ride for both the driver and passengers.

Safety is also a top priority in the 2018 Ford Taurus SE. Equipped with advanced features such as blind spot monitoring, lane departure warning, and rearview camera, you can drive with confidence and peace of mind. Plus, with its sturdy build and reliable braking system, you can trust this car to keep you and your loved ones safe on the road.

But that's not all, the 2018 Ford Taurus SE also boasts a sleek and modern exterior design, with smooth curves and a bold front grille. This car is sure to turn heads wherever you go, making a statement of style and sophistication.

Don't miss your chance to own the 2018 Ford Taurus SE. With its powerful engine, comfortable interior, advanced safety features, and stylish design, this car has it all. This 2018 Chevrolet Malibu LT is a sleek and sophisticated sedan that offers an exceptional driving experience. Powered by a 1.5L DOHC engine paired with a 6-Speed Automatic transmission, this Malibu delivers an impressive 27 city/36 highway MPG, making it both efficient and enjoyable to drive.

The exterior of this Malibu is adorned in a stunning White color, further enhanced by the premium 18-inch aluminum wheels. Step inside, and you'll be greeted by a spacious and well-appointed interior, featuring luxurious leather-appointed seating, a Bose premium 9-speaker sound system, and a host of advanced technology features.

The Convenience and Technology Package adds even more convenience and connectivity, with a remote vehicle starter system, wireless charging, and dual USB charging ports in the rear. The Leather Package elevates the driving experience with heated front seats, a power-adjustable front passenger seat, and an auto-dimming rearview mirror.

This Malibu is also equipped with a wide array of safety features, including ABS brakes, electronic stability control, and a rear-view camera, ensuring you and your passengers can travel with confidence.

Whether you're commuting to the office or embarking on a road trip, this 2018 Chevrolet Malibu LT is the perfect companion. Its blend of style, technology, and performance make it a standout in the midsize sedan segment. We invite you to experience the quality and value of this exceptional vehicle for yourself.

Our Best Price! First Time, Every Time!
Our sales people understand that buying a new or used vehicle can be a stressful experience. After all, statistics show that, after a home, an automobile is the biggest investment most of us will ever make. And, with most car dealers you are forced to enter a haggling/negotiating game to TRY to get the best deal possible.

It's just too much!!
But that is not the case at Quality Toyota. Our commitment to Bottom Line Pricing means that you get Our Best Price the first time, every time. You get our best price even before you talk to a sales person because Our Best Price is posted in the window of every vehicle on our lot.

The No Hassle/No Haggle Way to Buy a Car, SUV, or Truck
The fact that it is unnecessary to spend a great deal of time negotiating means that our salespeople can place emphasis where it belongs, finding the best possible vehicle for you, based on your needs and budget. After we find that vehicle (which will already have Our Best Price), we can focus on ensuring that you are completely satisfied with your purchase. So, come in and experience the Quality Toyota difference today!

description:
Discover the remarkable 2018 Toyota Corolla LE, a vehicle that seamlessly blends style, comfort, and cutting-edge technology. This stunning Corolla, finished in the eye-catching Blizzard Pearl exterior, is more than just a reliable commuter – it's a testament to Toyota's commitment to excellence.

Highlighted features include:
- Special Color - Blizzard Pearl
- Tilt & Slide Moonroof
- Exterior Parking Camera Rear
- Auto High-beam Headlights
- Heated Door Mirrors
- LED Daytime Running Lights (DRL)

Step inside and experience the refined interior, where every detail has been thoughtfully designed to enhance your driving experience. The Entune Audio Plus system with Connected Navigation keeps you connected and entertained, while the automatic temperature control and power windows ensure your comfort. The split-folding rear seat and ample cargo space provide the versatility to accommodate your lifestyle.

Powered by a 1.8L I4 DOHC engine and paired with a continuously variable transmission (CVT), the Corolla LE delivers an impressive 28 city/36 highway MPG, making it an exceptional choice for your daily commute or weekend adventures. The front-wheel-drive system and independent suspension provide a smooth, responsive ride, while the advanced safety features, including ABS brakes, dual front and side impact airbags, and Electronic Stability Control, give you peace of mind on the road.

We understand that finding the right vehicle is a significant decision, which is why we're committed to providing you with a hassle-free and personalized buying experience. Our team of knowledgeable professionals is here to answer any questions you may have and ensure that you drive away in the perfect Corolla LE to suit your needs.

Experience the exceptional craftsmanship and uncompromising performance of the 2018 Toyota Corolla LE. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate why this remarkable vehicle should be your next automotive companion.

Thoughtfully designed with your needs in mind, the Fusion Hybrid S offers ample storage and versatility. The split-folding rear seat allows you to easily accommodate larger items, while the generous cargo space ensures you can bring along all your essentials.

Experience the perfect fusion of efficiency, technology, and style with this 2018 Ford Fusion Hybrid S. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this exceptional vehicle can elevate your driving experience.

description: 2018 Chrysler 300 Touring — Bright White Clear Coat exterior with a Black interior. Powered by the Pentastar 3.6L V6 producing 292 hp and 260 lb-ft of torque, paired with an 8-speed automatic transmission for smooth, confident performance. This configuration delivers an EPA-rated 19 MPG city and 30 MPG highway. This 300 Touring is finished in Bright White Clear Coat and presents in excellent overall condition with a clean CARFAX report. The exterior carries Chrysler’s distinctive, upscale sedan styling — a bold grille, sculpted sheetmetal and alloy wheels — providing a composed, roadworthy presence. Inside, the Black cabin is roomy and practical, seating five with supportive front seats and a generous rear seat for adult passengers. Factory equipment includes a comprehensive set of convenience and comfort features: power windows and locks, remote keyless entry, power-adjustable driver’s seating, steering-wheel-mounted audio and cruise controls, and automatic climate control to keep the cabin comfortable for all occupants. The factory infotainment package provides Chrysler’s user-focused Uconnect system with Bluetooth hands-free calling and audio streaming, AUX/USB connectivity, and voice command functionality for phone and media control. Audio is delivered through the factory sound system tuned for balanced in-cabin listening. Standard safety and security features from the factory include multiple airbags (front, side and curtain), anti-lock brakes (ABS), electronic stability and traction control, a rearview backup camera, and tire pressure monitoring — all intended to provide confident day-to-day driving. This 300 Touring combines V6 power, comfortable interior space, and a well-rounded factory feature set in a clean, well-maintained package. Contact for additional details or to schedule a viewing. With a Carfax report available, you can purchase this beauty with confidence, knowing its history is transparent. Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this fantastic Fusion Hybrid - come take it for a spin today! description: Unleash your driving potential with the 2018 Chevrolet Cruze LT Auto, a compact powerhouse that's engineered to deliver performance and efficiency without compromise. With a robust 1.4L Turbo I4 engine cranking out 153 horsepower and 177 lb-ft of torque, this beauty not only offers a thrilling ride but also ensures you conquer the road with confidence. Draped in an eye-catching Summit White exterior, the Cruze commands attention wherever you go. Its sleek lines and bold stance make a striking impression, while the aerodynamic design enhances fuel efficiency, allowing you to slice through the air with ease. This vehicle is not just about looks, it’s built for the long haul, achieving an impressive 29 MPG in the city and an astounding 40 MPG on the highway. Say goodbye to frequent stops at the pump and hello to more time on the road. Step inside, and you'll find a meticulously crafted interior that doesn't skimp on comfort or style. The Dark Atmosphere/Medium Atmosphere color scheme creates a modern and inviting environment, perfect for both daily commutes and weekend adventures. The spacious cabin is designed with you in mind, featuring supportive seating and ample cargo space for all your gear. Equipped with a suite of factory-default features, the Cruze LT Auto is designed to elevate your driving experience. Enjoy the convenience of a 7-inch touchscreen infotainment system, complete with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto compatibility, allowing you to seamlessly connect your devices and access your favorite apps. The rearview camera enhances safety while maneuvering in tight spaces, and the available remote start system ensures you step into a perfectly pre-conditioned vehicle every time. Stay comfortable on the road with automatic climate control, and experience the rich sound of the six-speaker audio system that brings your music to life. Safety is paramount, and the Cruze comes loaded with advanced features including a suite of airbags, stability control, and a tire pressure monitoring system, giving you peace of mind every time you hit the road. This 2018 Chevrolet Cruze LT Auto is more than just a car, it’s a bold statement of performance, efficiency, and style. Don't let this opportunity pass you by – seize the wheel and dominate the road like never before!

description:
This 2018 Kia Optima LX is a standout choice for discerning drivers seeking a sophisticated and well-equipped sedan at a remarkable value. With its sleek exterior design, spacious interior, and impressive array of advanced features, this Optima delivers an exceptional driving experience that is sure to impress.

• Keyless Entry
• Back-Up Camera
• Convenience Package (Acoustic Laminated Front Door Windows, 10-Way Power Adjustable Driver's Seat, 2-way power lumbar support, Power Windows w/Front Auto Up/Down)
• 17" Alloy Wheels Package

Powered by a robust 2.4L I4 DGI DOHC engine and paired with a smooth-shifting 6-Speed Automatic with Sportmatic transmission, the Optima LX offers a dynamic and efficient performance, delivering an impressive 25 city/36 highway MPG. The well-appointed cabin features premium cloth seating, a 6.5" touchscreen audio system with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, and a host of convenience and safety technologies that elevate the driving experience.

The Optima's striking exterior is complemented by its well-appointed interior, which offers ample space and comfort for both driver and passengers. The 10-way power-adjustable driver's seat and available 17" alloy wheels add a touch of sophistication and style, while the acoustic laminated front door windows and rear parking sensors provide added convenience and peace of mind.

Safety is paramount in the Optima LX, with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assist technologies, including a rearview camera, electronic stability control, and a full array of airbags. This Kia is built to protect you and your loved ones, giving you the confidence to tackle the road ahead.

Whether you're commuting to work, embarking on a road trip, or simply enjoying the daily drive, this 2018 Kia Optima LX is an exceptional choice that delivers unbeatable value and a remarkable driving experience. Visit our showroom today to experience the Optima for yourself and discover why it's the perfect sedan for your lifestyle.

Buy with confidence at Zeigler Auto Group with every vehicle already equipped with our 3-year LoJack stolen vehicle recovery system, providing you with enhanced security and peace of mind. With LoJack, your car is protected against theft, ensuring quick recovery if needed. Drive confidently knowing your vehicle is safeguarded by one of the most trusted theft recovery systems available. Please note that a one-time fee of $699 will be added to the total cost.

This 2018 Volkswagen Jetta 1.4T SE is packed with premium features that will elevate your daily driving experience. From the stylish exterior in sleek Black to the well-appointed interior, this Jetta exudes sophistication and modern flair. Standout features include a power moonroof, heated front seats, and V-Tex leatherette upholstery, providing both comfort and refinement.

• MONSTER MATS W/LOGO RUBBER MAT KIT (SET OF 4)
• Heavy Duty Trunk Liner w/VW CarGo Blocks
• ROADSIDE ASSISTANCE KIT
• Power moonroof
• Heated door mirrors
• Power door mirrors
• Leather Shift Knob
• Heated Front Comfort Seats
• V-Tex Leatherette Seat Trim

Beneath the sleek exterior lies a responsive and efficient 1.4L TSI engine, paired with a smooth-shifting 6-speed automatic transmission with Tiptronic. This powertrain delivers an impressive 28 city/38 highway MPG, making it both fun and economical to drive. The Jetta's well-tuned suspension and precise steering also provide a dynamic and engaging driving experience, whether navigating city streets or cruising down the highway.

In addition to its premium features and performance, this Jetta also comes equipped with a host of advanced safety technologies, including a rearview camera, electronic stability control, and a comprehensive airbag system. These features work together to provide you and your passengers with the utmost protection on the road.

As a Certified Pre-Owned vehicle, this Jetta has undergone a rigorous inspection and reconditioning process, ensuring that it meets the highest standards of quality and reliability. With its low mileage of just 103,847, this Jetta has plenty of life left to offer its next owner.

If you're in the market for a practical and stylish daily driver or a versatile family vehicle, this 2018 Volkswagen Jetta 1.4T SE is an exceptional choice. We invite you to come in and experience it for yourself. Schedule a test drive today and discover the confidence and satisfaction that come with owning this exceptional Jetta.

Whether you are waiting for your vehicle to get serviced, picking up a part for your vehicle, or stopping by to check out a new vehicle for yourself, we offer a wide range of amenities to enhance your experience here! Come by, look around and check what we can offer you!

Preferred Equipment Group 1LT
    Convenience
    • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
    Safety and Security
    • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
    • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
    Technology and Telematics
    • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.

Step inside and be greeted by a spacious and comfortable cabin, featuring premium cloth seats and a leather-wrapped steering wheel. The Fusion SE also comes equipped with a 10-way power driver's seat, allowing you to find the perfect position for your daily commute or long road trips.

Stay connected on the go with the SYNC infotainment system, which includes voice-activated controls, Bluetooth connectivity, and a 4.2-inch LCD screen. Safety is also a top priority in the Fusion SE, with features such as a rearview camera, blind spot monitoring, and lane-keeping assist.

But that's not all, the 2018 Ford Fusion SE also boasts a sleek and modern exterior design, with chrome accents and available 18-inch machined aluminum wheels. With its bold and dynamic look, the Fusion SE is sure to turn heads wherever you go.

Don't miss out on the opportunity to own the 2018 Ford Fusion SE. Stop by our dealership today and take a test drive. Experience the perfect combination of style, performance, and technology in this exceptional sedan.

Discover the exceptional value and versatility of the 2018 Kia Rio S. This compact sedan offers an impressive blend of performance, technology, and convenience features that make it an outstanding choice for the savvy driver.

Highlighted by its sleek exterior design and well-appointed interior, the Rio S is packed with an array of desirable amenities:

• 6 Speakers
• SiriusXM Radio
• MP3 Audio System
• Air Conditioning
• Rear Window Defroster
• Bluetooth® Wireless Technology
• Power Steering
• Power Windows
• Remote Keyless Entry
• Steering Wheel Mounted Audio Controls
• Speed-Sensing Steering
• Traction Control
• ABS Brakes
• Dual Front Airbags
• Dual Front Side Impact Airbags
• Front Anti-Roll Bar
• Front Wheel Independent Suspension
• Brake Assist
• Electronic Stability Control
• Rear View Camera

Powered by a 1.6L I4 DGI 16V engine and paired with a 6-speed automatic transmission, the Rio S delivers an impressive EPA-estimated 28 city/37 highway mpg, making it an exceptionally fuel-efficient choice for your daily commute or weekend adventures.

Beyond its impressive performance and efficiency, the Rio S also boasts a host of advanced safety features, including a Panic Alarm, Speed Control, and Fully Automatic Headlights, providing you and your passengers with added peace of mind on the road.

With a sleek, modern design, a well-appointed interior, and a wealth of advanced features, the 2018 Kia Rio S represents an exceptional value in the compact sedan segment. Priced at just $11,000, this versatile and well-equipped vehicle is an outstanding choice for the discerning driver seeking a stylish, practical, and affordable transportation solution.

We invite you to experience the 2018 Kia Rio S for yourself. Visit our showroom today and let our knowledgeable sales team demonstrate how this exceptional compact sedan can meet your driving needs and exceed your expectations. We're confident that once you take it for a test drive, you'll be convinced that the Rio S is the perfect fit for your lifestyle.

Discover the exceptional value and refined driving experience of this 2018 Honda Accord LX. With its striking Platinum White Pearl exterior, this Accord LX offers a compelling blend of style, efficiency, and advanced technologies that make it an exceptional choice in the midsize sedan segment.

• 1.5T I4 DOHC 16V Turbocharged VTEC engine
• CVT transmission
• Front-wheel drive
• 30 city/38 highway MPG
• Automatic temperature control
• Steering wheel mounted audio controls
• Rear view camera
• Keyless entry
• Alloy wheels

Powered by a turbocharged 1.5-liter engine, the Accord LX delivers an engaging and responsive driving experience, while the CVT transmission ensures smooth, efficient power delivery. With an EPA-estimated 30 city and 38 highway MPG, this Accord LX will keep you on the road longer between fill-ups, making it a smart choice for your daily commute or weekend adventures.

Inside, the well-appointed cabin showcases Honda's commitment to quality and attention to detail.
